Service mesh (Istio/Linkerd) provides without code changes:
- **mTLS**: automatic certificate rotation, encrypted service-to-service traffic
- **Retries**: configurable retry policies per route
- **Circuit breaking**: outlier detection and ejection
- **Distributed tracing**: automatic span propagation via headers
- **Traffic splitting**: canary deployments (send 5% of traffic to new version)

