### Session vs JWT
| | Session-Based | JWT |
|--|--------------|-----|
| Storage | Server (Redis/DB) | Client (cookie/header) |
| Scalability | Need shared store | Stateless (any server) |
| Revocation | Easy (delete session) | Hard (need blocklist) |
| Size | Small session ID | Larger (payload) |

### RBAC (Role-Based Access Control)
